{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Shopify AI Command: The Grounded Heritage Section
    
    1. Layout & Architecture:
    
        Create a two-column custom section with a 60/40 split (60% text on the left, 40% outcomes on the right).
    
        Background: Match the "House of Vuu" sanctuary palette (clean off-white or light cream).
    
        Padding: Set Top and Bottom Padding to 100px for a "Quiet Luxury" feel.
    
    2. Narrative Content (Left Column):
    
        Eyebrow: THE HERITAGE (Manrope, All-Caps, 14px, 2px letter-spacing).
    
        Headline: A Legacy of Real Transformation (Bodoni Moda, Bold).
    
        Body Copy: "My journey—from arriving as a refugee to the global stages of fashion—taught me that true style is more than a look; it’s a foundation. From the red carpets of Cannes to the boardrooms of industry leaders, I’ve seen that when your identity is clear, your influence is unshakeable. This isn't just about clothing; it’s about aligning who you are with how the world sees you. We don't just dress the leader; we strengthen the person behind the title." (Manrope, 18px).
    
    3. Value Outcomes (Right Column):
    
        Create a vertical list of "Outcome Blocks." Each block should have a small checkmark icon (✔) or a thin vertical line as a bullet.
    
        Point 1: RESTORED CONFIDENCE: Lead with natural authority instead of performing a role.
    
        Point 2: STRATEGIC STYLE: A visual presence that commands the room before you speak.
    
        Point 3: LASTING IMPACT: Aligning your professional success with your personal values.
    
        Styling: Use Manrope for these points. The bolded titles should be 16px and the descriptions 14px.
    
    4. The Call to Action (CTA):
    
        Place a button at the bottom of the left column.
    
        Button Text: "LET'S START THE CONVERSATION"
    
        Style: Ghost / Outline Button (1px Black Border, Transparent background).
    
        Shape: Sharp 90-degree corners.
    
        Typography: Manrope, All-Caps, 14px, 2px letter-spacing.
    
    5. Mobile Optimization:
    
        Ensure columns stack vertically on mobile.
    
        Center-align all text and the button for the mobile view.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-heritage-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-heritage-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }

  .ai-heritage-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60% 40%;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .ai-heritage-left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .ai-heritage-eyebrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Manrope', {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-heritage-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Bodoni Moda', {{ block.settings.heading_font.family }}, serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-heritage-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Manrope', {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-heritage-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-heritage-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    font-family: 'Manrope', {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    background-color: transparent;
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.button_border_color }};
    border-radius: 0;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-heritage-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text }};
  }

  .ai-heritage-right-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .ai-heritage-outcome-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .ai-heritage-outcome-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .ai-heritage-outcome-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .ai-heritage-outcome-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Manrope', {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
  }

  .ai-heritage-outcome-desc-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: 'Manrope', {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-heritage-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
    }

    .ai-heritage-left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      text-align: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .ai-heritage-right-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .ai-heritage-outcome-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .ai-heritage-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-heritage-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .ai-heritage-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top | times: 0.6 }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<ai-heritage-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-heritage-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-heritage-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-heritage-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-heritage-left-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.eyebrow != blank %}
          <p class="ai-heritage-eyebrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.eyebrow }}</p>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.headline != blank %}
          <h2 class="ai-heritage-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.headline }}</h2>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.body_copy != blank %}
          <div class="ai-heritage-body-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.body_copy }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.cta_text != blank %}
          <a href="{{ block.settings.cta_link }}" class="ai-heritage-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.cta_text }}
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="ai-heritage-right-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.outcome_1_title != blank %}
          <div class="ai-heritage-outcome-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-heritage-outcome-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">✔</div>
            <div class="ai-heritage-outcome-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h3 class="ai-heritage-outcome-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.outcome_1_title }}</h3>
              {% if block.settings.outcome_1_desc != blank %}
                <p class="ai-heritage-outcome-desc-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.outcome_1_desc }}</p>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.outcome_2_title != blank %}
          <div class="ai-heritage-outcome-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-heritage-outcome-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">✔</div>
            <div class="ai-heritage-outcome-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h3 class="ai-heritage-outcome-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.outcome_2_title }}</h3>
              {% if block.settings.outcome_2_desc != blank %}
                <p class="ai-heritage-outcome-desc-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.outcome_2_desc }}</p>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if block.settings.outcome_3_title != blank %}
          <div class="ai-heritage-outcome-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-heritage-outcome-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">✔</div>
            <div class="ai-heritage-outcome-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h3 class="ai-heritage-outcome-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.outcome_3_title }}</h3>
              {% if block.settings.outcome_3_desc != blank %}
                <p class="ai-heritage-outcome-desc-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.outcome_3_desc }}</p>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</ai-heritage-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class AiHeritageSection{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.style.display = 'block';
      }
    }

    customElements.define('ai-heritage-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}', AiHeritageSection{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

